item.title: About Me
item.description: Hello! I’m Bryan Wassel, a passionate network engineer with over 15 years of experience in the IT industry, including more than 6 years specializing in Network Engineering. I have a knack for making complex systems simple and reliable, and I’ve had the pleasure of working on a variety of exciting projects that have sharpened my skills and expanded my knowledge. At Portkey, my goal is to create a space where people can learn and explore different topics in network engineering.
